{"type": "article", "id": 28199, "title": "咖啡套装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-15T06:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151903mv40NDQbacqxIKhw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你打算在家喝上一杯自己研磨的咖啡，意大利工作室 <a href=\"http://www.somethingdesign.com/\">Something</a> 最近为丹麦品牌 Stelton 设计的 Collar 是一套既满足了实用性又很美观的咖啡套装。Collar 包含了咖啡研磨机、糖碗、牛奶壶以及浓缩咖啡机，外观均为黑色的圆柱体，带给人一种朴素的质感。Collar 还有一些贴心的小细节，比如浓缩咖啡机采用木制把手，防止被烫伤。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151900gC0V74nxbLScDXQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80021368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519010X8tU1QxHsjOb7wW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151901h0OoA6tqyVF8En4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151902ylBsivPSOZq72MmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}